	orkshops-at-best-of-the-northwest-art-show/18318379/2026-04-12T00
LOCATION:Magnuson Park Hangar 30\, 6310 NE 74th St.\, Seattle\, WA
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:seatoday-arts
CATEGORIES:SEAtoday - Arts & Culture
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT3H
