BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:kwP4CI5TLdon8y5krS8gj
SUMMARY:Earlybirds Club
DTSTAMP:20260404T111405Z
DTSTART:20260502T003000Z
DESCRIPTION:Earlybirds Club is a dance party designed for women\, trans\, a
	nd non-binary folks that starts at 6pm and ends at 10pm because we have sh
	*t to do in the morning!At 2000s Night\, were bringing peak Y2K energy: fl
	ip phones out\, low-rise trauma healed\, and the hits that defined a gener
	ation. From Britney to Beyonc\, and from OutKast to Missy Elliott this is 
	a scream-sing\, drop-it-like-its-hot\, why do I still know every word? sit
	uation.Earlybirds Club is more than a night out its a judgment-free\, joy-
	forward space where kindness\, good vibes\, and sensible footwear rule. Co
	me as you are (Juicy tracksuits welcome\, comfy kicks encouraged) theres p
	lenty of room on the dance floor for everyone.10% of ticket proceeds benef
	it Refugee Artisan Initiative\, which partners with refugee and immigrant 
	women to build skills\, launch small businesses\, and craft sustainable pr
	oducts that empower communities and protect our planet. Note: By purchasin
	g these tickets\, you are consenting to be photographed for promotional pu
	rposes. People of all backgrounds and identities are encouraged to attend 
	all of our events.\nThis event is 21 and over. Any ticket holder unable to
	 present valid identification indicating that they are at least 21 years o
	f age will not be admitted to this event\, and will not be eligible for a 
	refund. All sales are final. There are no refunds unless the event is canc
	elled or postponed Opening Acts are subject to change or cancelation at an
	y time without notice. No refund will be owed if an Opening Act is changed
	 or canceled. Doors times subject to change Tickets may not be resold or o
	ffered for resale. If we suspect tickets have been purchased for resale pu
	rposes only\, we reserve the right to void or cancel the tickets without r
	efund. Tickets obtained from unauthorized sources may be invalid\, lost\, 
	stolen or counterfeit and if so\, are void.\nPrice: $42.3 - $42.3\n\nhttps
	://www.ticketweb.com/event/earlybirds-club-the-crocodile-tickets/14179344\
	n\nFrom The Crocodile
URL:https://www.ticketweb.com/event/earlybirds-club-the-crocodile-tickets/1
	4179344
